components.name: ButtonComponent
DatalistComponent
components.template:
<ipt-input
  [placeHolder]="placeHolder"
  [validateText]="validateText"
  [list]="datalistId"
  [control]="formControl.controls['dataListControl']"
  [inputType]="'text'"
  (change)="optionChanged($event)"
></ipt-input>

<datalist id="{{ datalistId }}">
  <option *ngFor="let item of datalistData; index as i" [value]="item.name">
    {{item.name}} {{item.last_name}}
  </option>
</datalist>

components.name: InputComponent
components.template: {{ validateText }}

components.name: SelectComponent

modules.name: DesignSystemModule

variables.name: exampleData
variables.defaultValue:
[
  { code: 1, name: 'Opcion 1' },
  { code: 2, name: 'Opcion 2' },
  { code: 3, name: 'Opcion 3' },
]
